highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 150 weeks straight.
“Watermelon Sugar” by Harry Styles is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #21.
J Balvin has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “RITMO (Bad Boys For Life)” is the highest at #9.
“everything i wanted” by Billie Eilish is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 100 spots at #2.
